OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry at first
OL,6,Fwith some hazy evening sunshine. It
OL,7,Fwill stay dry overnight, turning
OL,8,Fcloudy over northern Angus with some
OL,9,Fclear spells over Tayside and Fife.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FIt will be dry throughout the
OL,12,Fday with variable cloud and some warm
OL,13,Fsunny spells, locally very warn across
OL,14,Fthe west.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,17,Fagain on Tuesday with variable cloud
OL,18,Fand some warm sunny spells. Variable
OL,19,Fcloud and sunny spells on Wednesday
OL,20,Fand Thursday with the odd light shower
OL,21,Fat times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
